# WeChat status drafts. From R8 (2026-05-25) onwards these stay LOCAL —
# the persistent team-visible record is docs/DEV_LOG.md instead. See
# docs/POLICY.md §"Team status updates". Patterns cover the historical
# filename shape (WECHAT_UPDATE_*.md) and any future scratch dir.
